          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersIntro-A126"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Poison (Ex):</strong></span> Injury, Fortitude DC 22, initial damage 1d6 Str, secondary damage 2d6 Str. The save DC is Constitution-based.</p>
